title: Did the protestors of March attack a woman carrying the flag of Trump 2020?
subtitle: The activist Isabella DeLuca claimed that she was "blowed in the face and strangled by two women" just because she carried the flag of Trump 2020.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: On 17 October, women demonstrators in March in Washington, D.C., assaulted Isabella Deluca for carrying the Trump 2020 flag.
